## ansible create multiple users in loop


---
- name: create users
  hosts: all
  become: yes

  vars:
    users:   
      - dev1
      - dev2
      - dev3


  tasks:
    - name: create users
      user:
        name: "{{item}}"
	state: present
      loop: "{{users}}"


